PrecisAppointment of Marie-Andrée Lalonde-Morisset, of Île-des-Soeurs, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years and designation of the said Marie-Andrée Lalonde-Morisset as a coordinating member of the said Board.
